{
  "chapter": "041",
  "title": "越王句践世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>，他的祖先是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span>，是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">夏后</span>帝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">少康</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶子</span>。被<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>，用以奉守<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的祭祀。他们纹身断发，披荆斩棘开辟<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">草莱</span>而建立城邑。经过<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十多代（时长）</span>，传到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">允常</span>。注云：\"於，是发语之声。\""
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">允常</span>在位之时，与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">交战</span>而相互怨恨<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">允常</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>继位，这就是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>听闻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">允常</span>之死，于是兴兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>派遣<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">死士</span>前往挑<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，排成<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三行</span>，走到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军阵前，高呼口号后自刎。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军驻足观看，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>军趁机<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">偷袭</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">槜李</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战败</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>被箭射伤。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>临<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>之时，告诫其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span>说：\"千万不要忘记<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国。\""
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>听闻<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span>日夜操练军队，将要报复<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国想抢在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国未出兵之前先去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>劝谏道：\"不可。臣听说<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>是凶<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">器</span>，战争是违背德行之事，争斗是末流之事。阴谋违德，喜好使用凶<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">器</span>，在末流之事上亲自试验，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">上帝</span>禁止这样做，行动起来不会有利。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>说：\"我已经决定了。\"于是兴兵出征。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>得知此事，倾其全部精<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夫椒</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span>越军。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>便率残余<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千人</span>退保于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>山。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追击</span>并<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围困</span>了他。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>说：\"因为不听你的话才落到这个地步，该怎么办？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：范蠡\">蠡（范蠡）</span>回答说：\"持满盈者顺乎天，稳定倾危者顺乎人，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">节</span>制事务者顺乎地。用谦卑的言辞、丰厚的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>物去赠送他；如果不答应，就亲身前往作为人质交换。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>说：\"好。\""
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "于是派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>前往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国议和，跪着前行叩头说：\"您的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君王</span>的流亡之臣<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陪臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>冒昧告知您的下属：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>请求做臣下，其妻做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妾</span>。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>打算答应。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>说：\"上天把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国赐给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，不要答应。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>回来，把情况报告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀死</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻子</span>儿女，烧毁<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝器</span>，与吴军决<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">战死</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>阻止<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>贪婪，可以用利益引诱他，请让我暗中前去对他说。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>带美女和<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝器</span>暗中献给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>接受了，便引见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>去见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>叩头说：\"希望<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>的罪过，他将把所有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝器</span>都献上。如果不幸得不到<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>将把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻子</span>儿女全部<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀死</span>，烧毁所有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝器</span>，率<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千人</span>与吴决<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，必定会有相当的伤亡。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>趁机劝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国已经降服为臣，如果<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span>他们，这对我国有利。\""
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>打算答应。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>进谏说：\"现在不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，将来必定后悔。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤君</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：范蠡\">蠡（范蠡）</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">良臣</span>，如果返国，必将作乱。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>不听，最终<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，收兵回国。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>被困<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>时，慨然叹息说：\"我难道就此完结了吗？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>被囚禁于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夏台</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>被囚禁于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">羑里</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">重耳</span>逃奔翟地，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">小白</span>逃奔莒地，最终都成就了<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">王霸</span>之业。由此看来，现在的困境怎么就不能成为福气呢？\""
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国已<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国后，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>返回本国，就劳苦其身、忧思其志，在座位上悬挂<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">胆</span>，起坐都仰视<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">胆</span>，饮食时也先尝一口<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">胆</span>。他说：\"你忘记<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>的耻辱了吗？\"亲自耕种劳作，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>亲自纺织，吃饭不加<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">肉</span>食，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>不穿多色<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">采</span>服，屈身<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">节</span>礼对待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤人</span>，厚待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>，救济<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贫</span>困、吊唁<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死者</span>，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>同甘共苦。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "想让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>掌管国政，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：范蠡\">蠡（范蠡）</span>回答说：\"在用兵作战方面，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>不如我<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：范蠡\">蠡（范蠡）</span>；在安抚国家、亲附<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>方面，我<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：范蠡\">蠡（范蠡）</span>不如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>。\"于是把全国<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>事托付给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>，而让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">柘稽</span>前往议和，作为人质住在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>后<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国放<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：范蠡\">蠡（范蠡）</span>归国。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>归国已<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七年（时长）</span>，安抚其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士民</span>，想要任用他们去报复<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">逢同</span>进谏道：\"我国新近流亡复起，如今才渐渐充实，如果整治武备使之精良，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国必定畏惧，一畏惧则祸难必至。况且鸷<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟</span>攻击猎物时，必定隐匿其<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">形</span>。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>锋加于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国，对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国怨恨更深，名声高于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，实际上已危害<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>王室，德薄而功多，必然骄矜放纵。为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国打算，不如结交<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国、亲近<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国、依附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国、厚待<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国野心广大，必会轻率<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">开战</span>。这样我国联合其他诸国之力，三国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span>它，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国趁其疲敝之机，可以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战胜</span>它。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>说：\"好。\""
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>将要伐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>劝谏说：\"不可。臣听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>吃饭不用两味菜，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>同甘共苦。此人不死，必为我国之患。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，是<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">腹心之疾</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国对于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，不过是疥癣之疾。希望王放弃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国先攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>不听，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">艾陵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span>齐军，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：高张\">高（高张）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：国书\">国（国书）</span>凯旋归国。回来后责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>说：\"王不要高兴！\"王大怒，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>，王听说后阻止了他。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">越大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>说：\"我观察<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>事已经骄傲了，请试着向他借粮食，以此卜测其事。\"请求借粮，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>想给，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>劝谏不要给，王最终给了，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国私下里暗喜。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>说：\"王不听劝谏，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>后<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国恐怕要成为废墟了！\""
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>听闻此事，多次与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>就<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国的议题争论，于是中伤<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍员</span>表面忠诚实际上心狠，他连自己的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父兄</span>都不顾，怎能顾得上王？王以前想伐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍员\">员（伍员）</span>极力劝阻，事后得胜有功，他反而因此怨恨王。王若不防备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍员</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍员\">员（伍员）</span>必定作乱。\"他与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">逢同</span>一起谋划，在王面前进谗。王起初不信，后来派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国，听说他把儿子托付给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲍氏</span>，王大怒，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍员</span>果然欺骗<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>！\"出使归来后，派人赐给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">属镂剑</span>让他<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>大笑说：\"我让你父亲称霸，又拥立你，你当初想把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国一半分给我，我不接受，现在你反而因谗言<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>我。唉，唉，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>固然不能独立成事！\"他对使者说：\"一定要把我的眼睛放在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东门</span>上，让我看到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国兵马攻入！\"从此<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国把<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>权交给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国已经<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>，迎合阿谀之人众多，可以动手了吗？\"回答说：\"还不行。\"到了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年春</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>北上在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄池</span>会盟<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国精锐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>卒都随王前往，只留下老弱和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>守国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>再问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：范蠡\">蠡（范蠡）</span>说：\"可以了。\""
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "于是派出习水战的士卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千人</span>、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">教士</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四万人</span>、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>近卫<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六千人</span>、各种御者<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千人</span>，去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战败</span>，于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国向王告急，王正在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄池</span>会盟<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，怕<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>诸侯听到此事，就隐秘不发。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>完成<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄池</span>会盟后，派人带厚礼向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国请和。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国自度也还不能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，就与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国讲和。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "此后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国再次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士民</span>疲惫不堪，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">轻锐</span>都已<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">战死</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>战场。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军，接着围困吴都<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>溃，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国再次把<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>困在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">姑苏之山</span>。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙雄</span>袒露上身跪行到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>前，请求议和说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孤臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span>斗胆披露心事：从前曾得罪于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span>不敢违命，得以与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君王</span>讲和而归。如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君王</span>抬起<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉趾</span>前来<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孤臣</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孤臣</span>唯命是听，不知<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君王</span>是否也愿像当年<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>时那样<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孤臣</span>的罪过呢？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>不忍心，想答应他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>之事，上天把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国赐给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国没有接受。如今上天把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国赐给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国怎能违逆天意呢？况且<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君王</span>早起晚归操劳，不都是为了对付<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国吗？谋划了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一旦</span>放弃，可以吗？况且<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">天与弗取，反受其咎</span>。'伐柯者其则不远'（砍斧柄的范式就在眼前），君难道忘了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>之困吗？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>说：\"我想听你的话，但不忍心对吴国使者说出口。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>于是击鼓进<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>，说：\"王已将<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>务托付给我，使者请离去，不然将获罪。\""
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国使者哭泣而去。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>怜悯他，于是派人告诉<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>说：\"我把王安置在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甬东</span>，让您治理<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">百家</span>。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>推辞说：\"我已经老了，不能再侍奉<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君王</span>了！\"于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。自杀时遮住自己的脸，说：\"我没有脸去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子胥</span>！\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>于是葬了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span>，并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国后，率<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>北渡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徐州</span>会盟，向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>王室进贡。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周元王</span>派人赐给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>祭肉，封他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">伯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>离开<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徐州</span>后，渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>南岸，把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上地</span>送给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国侵占的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>国土地归还<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>国，送给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗东</span>方<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>之地。当时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>锋横行于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>以东，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都来祝贺，称为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">霸王</span>。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>离开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国后，从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国寄信给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>说：\"飞<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟</span>都打尽了，良<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弓</span>就要收起来了；狡<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">兔</span>都死光了，猎<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狗</span>就要被烹煮了。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>这个人长颈鸟喙，可以与他共患难，不可与他共享乐。你为何不离开？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>看了信，称病不上朝。有人进谗说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>将要作乱，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>就赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>一把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>说：\"你教<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>有七条计策，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>用了三条就<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，其余四条还在你那里，你替我去见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>试试吧。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>便<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>了。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>去世，其子<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鼫与</span>继位。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鼫与</span>去世，其子<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">不寿</span>继位。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">不寿</span>去世，其子<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">翁</span>继位。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">翁</span>去世，其子<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">翳</span>继位。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">翳</span>去世，其子<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">之侯</span>继位。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">之侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无彊</span>继位。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无彊</span>时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国兴兵北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，西<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>争强。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "当<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚威王</span>在位时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐威王</span>派人游说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，大而言之不能称王，小而言之不能称霸。推究<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国之所以不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的原因，是因为得不到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国（指三晋）的支持。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>本来就不会<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，会被覆其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">军</span>队，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>领被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>，那么<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">叶</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳翟</span>就危险了；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>也会被覆其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">军</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>其<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>，那么<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上蔡</span>也不得安宁。所以二<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>服事<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，不会到覆<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">军</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>的地步，连出点马汗的力气都做不到。您又何必看重得到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国的支持？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>说：\"我所要求于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>的，不是要他们动<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">刃</span>接<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>真正交战，更不用说<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>城<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>邑了。只希望<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国聚兵于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>之下，希望<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莒地</span>展示兵力，聚集于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郯</span>之境，那么<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">方城</span>以外的楚军就不能南下，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>之间的楚军就不能东进，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">商</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">於</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">析</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郦</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宗胡</span>这些地方，以及<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夏路</span>以西，都不足以防备<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江南</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗上</span>也不足以抵挡<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国了。这样，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>都能在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国得志，二<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>而分得土地，不耕而有收获。现在不这样做，却要在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河山</span>之间动<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">刃</span>兵为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐秦</span>所用，所期待的如此失计，何以因此称王！\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国使者说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国幸运啊还没灭亡！我不赞许它用智如同眼睛那样，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语·现代：目不见睫\">见豪毛而不见其睫（目不见睫）</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>知道<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国的失计，却不知自己<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国的过失，这是目论（只能看见远而不能看见近）。王所期待于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>的，并非希望他们出马汗之力，也不是要与他们合军联和，而是要借他们来分散<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的兵力。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国兵力已经分散，还期待<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>干什么呢？\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>说：\"那该怎么办？\"使者说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国三位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>分兵九<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">军</span>，北边围困<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲沃</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">於中</span>，一直到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">无假之关</span>延绵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千七百里</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景翠</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">军</span>队北集于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>，兵力分散得还有比这更严重的吗？况且王所希望的，是挑起<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>相斗；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>不相斗，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国也不发<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>，这是知二五而不知十啊。此时若不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，臣因此知道<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国大不王、小不伯。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">复雠</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">庞</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的产粮地；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">竟泽陵</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的木材地。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国只要出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>通过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">无假之关</span>，这四地便不再向<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>都进贡了。臣听说，图王而不成王，其次也可以称霸。然而不能称霸，就是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">王道</span>失败了。所以希望<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大王</span>转而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。\""
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国放弃攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>而转<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚威王</span>兴<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>伐越，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无彊</span>，尽<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>原<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国旧地直到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浙江</span>，北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徐州</span>。从此<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国散乱，诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">族子</span>争相自立，有的称王，有的称君，散居于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>南<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>上，臣服于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国。"
    },
    "29": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "其后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七世（时长）</span>，到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">闽君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：东越王摇\">摇（东越王摇）</span>时，辅助<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉高帝\">高帝（汉高帝）</span>再封<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：东越王摇\">摇（东越王摇）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span>，以奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国后嗣。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东越</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">闽君</span>，都是他的后代。"
    },
    "30": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>侍奉<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">越王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>，劳苦身心、尽力效命，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>深谋<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二十多年（时长）</span>，终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>掉强大的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，报了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>之耻，北渡<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>以威临<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>，号令<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>诸国，以尊崇<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>王室，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>因而称霸，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>被称为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将军</span>。回到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>认为大名之下难以长久安居，而且<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>为人可与共患难、难与处安乐，于是写信辞别<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>说：\"臣听说<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">主忧臣劳，主辱臣死</span>。从前<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君王</span>受辱于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>，臣之所以不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>，就是为了今天这件事。现在既已雪耻，请让我承担从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>以来应受的<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>罚。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孤</span>将与你分国共有。不然，就要加以<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>说：\"君按法令行事，臣按自己心意行事。\""
    },
    "31": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>打包轻便的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝珠玉</span>器，与其私人随从乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舟</span>浮<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>而去，终不返回。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>划出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽山</span>作为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>的供奉采邑。"
    },
    "32": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>浮<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>到达<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国，改名换姓，自称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鸱夷子皮</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>边耕作，劳苦身体、尽力致产，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父子</span>共同治产。居住不久，就积累产业<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十万</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国人听说他贤能，让他做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>慨然叹道：\"居家能致<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>，居官能至<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卿相</span>，这是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">布衣</span>之极啊。长久享受尊贵之名，不吉利。\""
    },
    "33": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "于是归还<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>印，散尽财物，分给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">知友乡党</span>，怀着贵重的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝</span>物，悄悄离去，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>地停下，认为此地是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的中心，交易四通八达，经营此处可以致富。于是自称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陶硃公</span>。再约束<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父子</span>耕作畜养，废时转物（囤积待售），获取十分之一的利润。居住不久，就资产累积巨万。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>人都称他为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陶硃公</span>。"
    },
    "34": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>地，生下<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span>长大成人时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">中男</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了人，被囚禁在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>说：\"<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>人偿<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>，是理所应当的。然而我听说<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>之家的子弟不应在市集上被处<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>。\"于是告诉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span>前去探视。就包装<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄金</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千溢</span>（镒，古代重量单位），放在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">褐器</span>中，用一辆<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">牛车</span>装载。将要遣送<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>坚决请求要去，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>不听。"
    },
    "35": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>说：\"家有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长子</span>称为家督（督察家事），如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>有罪，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大人</span>不派我去，却派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少弟</span>，这是我不肖。\"想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。他的母亲替他说：\"如今派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span>，未必能救活<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">中子</span>，却先白白失去<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>，怎么办呢？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>不得已而派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>去，写了一封信让他带给旧友<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>。说：\"到达后就把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>送到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>那里，任凭他的处置，千万不要与他争执。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>出发后，又私自带了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>。"
    },
    "36": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>家靠近外城墙，推开<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">藜藋</span>之草才能到门，住处甚为贫穷。然而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>还是按父亲的话，送上书信和<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>说：\"你可以快快离去，千万不要停留！等<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>出来，也不要问是什么原因。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>离去后，没有再经过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>家而私自留下来，把自己私带的钱财献给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国当权的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贵人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>虽住在穷巷，然而因廉直之名闻于全国，从<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>以下都尊他为师。等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>送<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>来，并非有意接受，只想事成后再归还以表信用。所以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>一送到，就对妻子说：\"这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>。我若有病突然去世未及告诫，事后再归还他，不要动用。\"而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>不知其意，以为送金之事毫无作用。"
    },
    "37": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>找机会入见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>，说：\"某<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">星</span>宿于某方位，这对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国有害。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>素来信任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>，说：\"现在该怎么办？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>说：\"只有用修德来消除它。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>说：\"先生请回吧，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>将去办。\"王于是派使者查封三钱之府（府库）。"
    },
    "38": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贵人</span>惊喜地告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>说：\"王将要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>免了。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>问：\"何以见得？\"回答说：\"每当王要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>免时，常常查封三钱之府。昨天晚上王已派人去查封了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>以为有<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>令，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>本来应当出来，那厚重的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>白白送给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>，毫无用处，于是又去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>吃惊说：\"你还没走吗？\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>说：\"没有。起初为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>来的，现在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>听说将要<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦</span>免，所以来辞别先生离去。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>知道他想拿回黄金，说：\"你自己入室拿回<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>吧。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>就自行入室把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>取走，暗自欢喜庆幸。"
    },
    "39": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄生</span>感到被小儿子所戏耍，于是入见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>说：\"臣先前禀告某<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">星</span>之事，王说要修德以回报。如今臣出门，道上都在说<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>地富人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>之子<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>人被囚于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，其家重<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金钱</span>贿赂王的左右，所以王并非真的体恤<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国而<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>免，而是因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>之子的缘故啊。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>大怒说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>虽无德行，怎会因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>之子的缘故而施此恩惠呢！\"便下令处<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>之子，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">第二天</span>才下达<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>令。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span>最终只能运<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>的灵柩归家。"
    },
    "40": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "到家后，母亲及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">邑人</span>都为之悲哀，唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>独自发笑，说：\"我早就知道他必会<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">害死</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>了！他并非不爱<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>，只是有些事他做不到而已。他年少时与我一同，见过困苦，深知谋生艰难，所以看重钱财。至于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少弟</span>，生下来就见我富足，乘坚车驱良马追逐狡<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">兔</span>，怎知钱财从何而来，所以视钱财为轻，并不吝惜。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">前日</span>我所以想派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span>去，正是因他能舍弃钱财。而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>做不到，所以最终害死了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>，事情的道理本当如此，没什么可悲伤的。我日夜本就等着丧讯到来。\"所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>三次迁徙，名成于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，并非徒然离去而已，他所停留的地方都能成名。最终老死于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>地，所以世人传称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陶硃公</span>。"
    },
    "41": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的功劳大啊，疏通九河，奠定<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九州</span>，直到今天诸<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>都安定。到了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>，劳苦身心、忧思国事，终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>掉强大的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，北观<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>，以尊崇<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>王室，号称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">霸王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>难道不算贤明吗？大概是有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的遗风吧。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>三次迁徙都获得荣名，名声流传后世。臣主如此，怎能不显达呢！"
    },
    "42": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国的祖先<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">少康</span>，传到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">允常</span>。 其子开始称霸，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国争强。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">槜李</span>之役，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖闾</span>身受<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">伤</span>。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>之耻，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>发誓要雪。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>以利诱敌，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：范蠡\">蠡（范蠡）</span>竭其才智。 屈身<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">节</span>礼待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，思尝<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">胆</span>以铭志。 终于<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">复雠</span>破敌，遂<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">殄</span>灭大邦。 后世不自量力，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无彊</span>。"
    }
  }
}